I would recommend that you no use the indices directly, but use the `Find()` method to locate the menu that you want.  This will work even if other menus are added or removed.  E.g., 

```
MathJax.Hub.Register.StartupHook("MathMenu Ready", function () {
  var renderers = MathJax.Menu.menu.Find("Math Settings").submenu.Find("Math Renderer").submenu;
  renderers.Find("SVG").disabled = true;
  renderers.Find("Fast HTML").disabled = true;
  renderers.Find("PlainSource").disabled = true;
});
```
Add any renderers that you don't include.  If you don't provide the AssistiveMML or Fast Preview code, then you should disable those as well.

